{"tid":1584001,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西鐵分別下午1時及3時起關閉屯門站及元朗站","createTime":"2019-09-21T02:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T03:52:41.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a663257a432322da4479279cf2d3456668c6c7","tid":1584001,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"因應有公眾活動進行，港鐵表示，在進行仔細風險評估，並與相關政府部門商討後，考慮到乘客及員工的安全，為審慎起見，西鐵綫列車服務會於稍後時間作出調整，由下午1時起，屯門站暫時關閉，列車不停屯門站。由下午3時起，元朗站亦會暫時關閉，列車同時不停元朗站。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵會視乎實際情況，基於乘客和員工的安全考慮，亦有可能隨時關閉其他車站或部分出入口，而未能預早通知。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵呼籲乘客預早計劃行程，及留意港鐵網頁、手機應用程MTR Mobile，車站及列車廣播發放的最新車務安排。"},{"pid":"7854d7766c06e45c8937af1a318c4d2fb47ea97b","tid":1584001,"uid":808,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"2d2e2972fa06046e1f186d3c1def2165e2c56fe0","tid":1584001,"uid":72775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:10:45.000Z","msg":"不意外 黨鐵"},{"pid":"7e920bbdd9521b1337330b6719104898b2406c7b","tid":1584001,"uid":48315,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:10:46.000Z","msg":"批不反對通知書就可以事前封站 等啲人去唔到"},{"pid":"86f8f5806cf331983cb7c6ef6ad697537c840a5a","tid":1584001,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e85804791af93a3a43935c8d969b35982d691a9","tid":1584001,"uid":320482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"有病"},{"pid":"8b0a3eeffd26fe4e19fe0956e37a72cc0f81bdb5","tid":1584001,"uid":78186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:10:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，早啲去"},{"pid":"1793e04cf78ad7b05d598d306e0cd3426b454aa2","tid":1584001,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":